\begin_layout Itemize
How about sufficiency? 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
In a general framework, the sufficient condition for valid instruments is given as follows.
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard

\begin_inset ERT
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

